description._content: Bain News Service,, publisher. Maj. Gen. W.H. Birkbeck [between ca. 1910 and ca. 1915] 1 negative : glass ; 5 x 7 in. or smaller. Notes: Title from data provided by the Bain News Service on the negative. Photograph shows General Sir William Henry Birkbeck (1863-1929), Director of Remounts at British Army Headquarters from 1912 to 1920. (Source: Flickr Commons project, 2012) Forms part of: George Grantham Bain Collection (Library of Congress). Format: Glass negatives. Rights Info: No known restrictions on publication.
